# eval_logs directory — eval reports are auto-generated here after each pipeline run

Each file is named:  eval_report_YYYY-MM-DD_HH-MM-SS.md
The latest report is always also available as:  latest.md

Reports include:
  - Timestamp and trigger source (post_pipeline / cli / manual)
  - Per-run summary table with grades
  - Contradiction Recall Eval: precision, recall, missed contradictions
  - Feedback Loop Regression Eval: test scores, failures, warnings
